==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Threadbare
<hw>Thread"bare`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Worn
to the naked thread; having the nap worn off; <xex>threadbare</xex>
clothes.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A <xex>threadbare</xex> cope.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Fig.: Worn out; <as>as, a <ex>threadbare</ex>
subject; stale topics and <ex>threadbare</ex> quotations.</as></def>
<rj><au>Swift.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Threadbareness</ent>⟦br⟧
